<Layout title="About | Francesco Esposito">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <header class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            About Me
          </h1>
          <span class="text-2xl ml-2">üë®‚Äçüíª</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
        <p>
          I'm Francesco Esposito, a software engineer with a passion for
          frontend development and creating intuitive user experiences. This is
          my personal space where I share what I learn and build to help others
          in their coding journey.
        </p>

        <h2>My Background</h2>
        <p>
          With over 10 years of experience in software development, I've worked
          on various web applications, focusing primarily on frontend
          technologies like React, TypeScript, and modern CSS.
        </p>

        <h2>Technical Skills</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>React & React Native</li>
          <li>TypeScript</li>
          <li>Modern CSS (Tailwind, styled-components)</li>
          <li>Node.js</li>
          <li>Web Performance Optimization</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What I'm Currently Learning</h2>
        <p>
          I'm currently exploring static site generators like Astro, improving
          my knowledge of web accessibility, and learning more about serverless
          architectures.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-8">Mentorship</h2>
        <p>
          I'm passionate about helping others grow in their careers. As a
          mentor, I provide guidance on:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Frontend development best practices</li>
          <li>Career advice and growth strategies</li>
          <li>Technical interview preparation</li>
          <li>Code reviews and architecture feedback</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">
          You can book a session with me on <a
            href="https://mentorcruise.com/mentor/FrancescoEsposito/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline"
